   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>(chi)(rho) List of things which I, Epiphanios, have lost--and I suspect the most reverent Hierios, son of Patrophilos:  the big key of the upper floor, two cypresses from the double-roof(?), six birds, a table.  When he emptied his apartment, I gave him two rooms to move into, and he did not give me those back (chi)(rho) (chi)(rho) Priest Epiphanios, son of Damianos--I have accepted the oath from the most reverent Hierios himself (or: from the same most reverent Hierios) (chi)(rho)</ab>
         </div>
